      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add chat picker search and pagination",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFollow-up to #85211. This keeps the chat session picker bounded while making older conversations reachable on demand.\n\n- Add `offset` support to `sessions.list` and return `offset`/`nextOffset` pagination metadata alongside the existing `totalCount`/`hasMore` fields.\n- Add chat picker search controls that use the existing server-side session `search` filter.\n- Add Load More support that appends additional `sessions.list` pages without duplicating rows.\n- Reduce the chat picker's initial page from 100 to 50 now that users can search or page deeper.\n- Add localized labels for the new picker controls.\n\n## Why\n\n#85211 removes the accidental active-window/current-agent filters so channel conversations are selectable again, but the picker still needs a hard cap to avoid repeating the older performance regression from broad session-store scans. Search plus offset pagination makes the bounded response an explicit UI behavior instead of a hidden truncation point.\n\nThis also addresses the review concern that the prior `limit: 0` path only fell back to the server default. The initial load is now deliberately bounded, and users can search or request another page when the conversation they need is not in the first result set.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `OPENCLAW_VITEST_NO_OUTPUT_TIMEOUT_MS=60000 OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.gateway.config.ts src/gateway/session-utils.test.ts`\n- `pnpm --dir ui exec vitest run --config vitest.config.ts --project unit src/ui/views/chat.test.ts src/ui/controllers/sessions.test.ts src/ui/app-chat.test.ts`\n- `pnpm --dir ui exec vitest run --config vitest.config.ts --project unit-node src/ui/app-gateway.sessions.node.test.ts src/ui/app-render.helpers.node.test.ts src/ui/app-gateway-chat-load.node.test.ts`\n- `pnpm ui:i18n:check`\n- `pnpm ui:build`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`",
        "branch": "codex/chat-picker-search-pagination",
